        "cooked": "<p>TN: 2002 De Courcel Grand Clos Des Epenots.<br>\nNot even remotely ready to drink, lovely nose but a hard palate of bitter cherry with a slighty green finish (stems perhaps), gave this plenty of time in the decanter and drank it over 3 hours but it kept getting tighter. will be a very very good wine with another 10 years on it</p>",
