        "created_at": "2017-06-04T19:35:58.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>The winemaking here is pretty bizarre to my mind. Great sites, great fruit. Pretty much everyone else has moved on from the Accad method, I wish Yves would too.</p>\n<p>Tasting there in the morning is a great way to brutalize the palate at the beginning of a long day of tasting.</p>",
